'This userform popsup when a new task is complete so that the user can see what it gained from XP, GP, Mana and prizes. It will close
'after 4 seconds or when the user clicks it.

Private Sub UserForm_Initialize()
Call RemoveCaption(Me)
End Sub

Private Sub UserForm_Activate()
Strt = Timer
Do While Timer < Strt + 4
    DoEvents
Loop
Me.Hide
End Sub

Private Sub Image2_Click()
Me.Hide
End Sub

Private Sub Image3_Click()
Me.Hide
End Sub

Private Sub Image4_Click()
Me.Hide
End Sub

Private Sub prizelabel_Click()
Me.Hide
End Sub

Private Sub xplabel_Click()
Me.Hide
End Sub

Private Sub mplabel_Click()
Me.Hide
End Sub

Private Sub gplabel_Click()
Me.Hide
End Sub

Private Sub splabel_Click()
Me.Hide
End Sub
